Growth rates were determined by measuring the number of cells in each well on the first and final days using a hemocytometer (Marienfeld, Germany). The specific growth rate (μ) was calculated using the following formula:μ=LN(N2N1)(t2−t1)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
